            "start_row_offset_idx": 0,
            "end_row_offset_idx": 0,
            "start_col_offset_idx": 0,
            "end_col_offset_idx": 0,
            "text": "Weather summary of preceding week- (02/01/25- 06/01/25)",
            "column_header": true,
            "row_header": false,
            "row_section": false,
            "fillable": false
          },
          {
            "row_span": 1,
            "col_span": 1,
            "start_row_offset_idx": 0,
            "end_row_offset_idx": 0,
            "start_col_offset_idx": 1,
            "end_col_offset_idx": 1,
            "text": "Weather forecast for the next 5 days (08/01/25- 12/01/25)",
            "column_header": true,
            "row_header": false,
            "row_section": false,
            "fillable": false
          },
          {
            "row_span": 1,
            "col_span": 1,
            "start_row_offset_idx": 1,
            "end_row_offset_idx": 1,
            "start_col_offset_idx": 0,
            "end_col_offset_idx": 0,
            "text": "During the preceding week, the maximum temperature was 35.0\u00b0C and the minimum temperature was 20.0\u00b0C. Relative humidity of 54 - 87 % was experienced. Speed of westerly winds was up to 2-4 km. No rainfall was received in Alappuzha district during the week.",
            "column_header": false,
            "row_header": false,
            "row_section": false,
            "fillable": false
          },
          {
            "row_span": 1,
            "col_span": 1,
            "start_row_offset_idx": 1,
            "end_row_offset_idx": 1,
            "start_col_offset_idx": 1,
            "end_col_offset_idx": 1,
            "text": "Dry weather expected for the next five days in Alappuzha district. The maximum temperature this week will be 29.7\u00b0C and the minimum temperature will be 23.5 \u00b0C. The atmospheric humidity will be between 52% and 90%. Westerly wind speed is likely to reach 6 km/h.",
            "column_header": false,
            "row_header": false,
            "row_section": false,
            "fillable": false
          }
        ],
        "num_rows": 2,
        "num_cols": 2,
